high_descs: Pick up the bread in front of the tomato.
Bring the bread to the microwave.
Heat the bread in the microwave.
Bring the bread to the counter by the coffee machine.
Put the bread on the counter in front of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Heat a loaf of bread, put it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your left, go forward and turn left to face the white table on your left.
Grab a loaf of bread off the table.
Turn left, go forward and turn left to the white stove on your left.
Put the loaf in the microwave for a bit and take it out.
Then turn to your right and then left to face the counter top
Put the loaf of bread down on the counter top to the right of the green wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Warm up a loaf of bread.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the corner on the other side of the room then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the loaf of bread that is between the other three loaves.
Turn left and walk to the front of the stove then turn and face it.
Place the bread in the microwave and heat it then remove it.
Turn right and walk to the counter with the frying pan on it then turn left to face the counter.
Place the bread on the counter to the right of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a loaf of bread.
